      "content": "That's really helpful, thanks. I guess I'm just worried about things that aren't super obvious. Like, are there any \"hidden\" risks or ways that these liabilities can sneak up on someone? Sometimes it feels like these contracts have these little traps where you think you're fine, then suddenly everything blows up. Is there anything specific I should be looking for to make sure I'm not walking into a trap?",
